316
00:51:20,273 --> 00:51:21,865
Then the nurse checked
the donor records

317
00:51:22,108 --> 00:51:24,941
And we realized that
you gave blood together

318
00:51:25,545 --> 00:51:27,206
Can I see my friend?

319
00:53:08,648 --> 00:53:09,706
Joy

320
