368
01:00:18,277 --> 01:00:19,471
The man has become zombie and

369
01:00:19,678 --> 01:00:20,804
the woman is a vengeful spirit

370
01:00:23,949 --> 01:00:26,315
So now you have to pay for it

371
01:00:28,988 --> 01:00:30,819
The ghost wants you

372
01:00:31,090 --> 01:00:33,388
to kill her boyfriend

373
01:00:33,793 --> 01:00:35,886
That's the only way
you can save your friend

374
01:00:41,567 --> 01:00:44,331
Don't worry. It's all right

375
01:00:44,570 --> 01:00:47,198
Mom is here. It's all right

376
01:00:47,439 --> 01:00:50,067
Don't be afraid...

377
01:01:31,217 --> 01:01:33,651
Lok, you have to help me.
Kill him!

378
01:02:22,735 --> 01:02:24,794
Stand up...

379
01:02:26,772 --> 01:02:27,864
Be good

380
01:02:50,729 --> 01:02:51,593
Paul! Fancy seeing you here!

381
01:02:51,797 --> 01:02:52,889
Yes, I'm checking on Joy

382
01:02:53,132 --> 01:02:54,121
See you around

383
01:02:55,834 --> 01:02:57,927
Be careful what you say

384
01:02:58,370 --> 01:03:00,600
I don't want anyone
to know about us

385
01:03:02,508 --> 01:03:06,308
I am the only person
who can keep you out of jail

386
01:03:14,253 --> 01:03:15,413
Understand?

387
01:03:20,025 --> 01:03:21,253
You're crazy!

388
01:03:26,732 --> 01:03:28,199
Yes, I'm crazy

389
01:03:29,902 --> 01:03:31,927
I could kill someone and
still not go to jail...

390
01:03:42,881 --> 01:03:45,076
This woman has
a severe psychotic condition

391
01:03:45,351 --> 01:03:46,579
She claims she always sees ghosts

392
01:03:47,086 --> 01:03:48,053
What should I do?

393
01:03:48,854 --> 01:03:51,186
Joy, how do you feel?

394
01:03:51,523 --> 01:03:54,185
Let us help you

395
01:03:59,665 --> 01:04:03,032
Joy, we can't help you
if you're like this

396
01:04:14,079 --> 01:04:16,479
Joy, you say you can see ghosts

397
01:04:16,715 --> 01:04:18,580
Can you tell us what they look like?

398
01:04:24,023 --> 01:04:25,923
It's an open and shut case.
We don't need to any more tests

399
01:04:27,893 --> 01:04:29,383
Are you looking for me?

400
01:04:37,069 --> 01:04:38,696
I'm Yau Yin Ping

401
01:04:41,740 --> 01:04:45,574
You won't understand
how a woman feels

402
01:04:45,811 --> 01:04:46,539
Someone enduring an incurable disease

403
01:04:46,812 --> 01:04:48,245
who wanted to die

404
01:04:48,514 --> 01:04:49,879
Together with her lover

405
01:04:52,484 --> 01:04:54,714
I didn't want to leave alone

406
01:04:55,687 --> 01:04:58,417
I wanted Jack to die with me

407
01:05:00,726 --> 01:05:03,160
That's why I cut myself so deep

408
01:05:04,630 --> 01:05:07,098
I can't be without him

409
01:05:12,471 --> 01:05:14,803
The three of you saved his life

410
01:05:15,007 --> 01:05:16,770
Listen to me.
No one can help them

411
01:05:17,009 --> 01:05:19,569
Whoever helps them has to die!

412
01:06:32,184 --> 01:06:33,310
Lok!

413
01:06:48,734 --> 01:06:49,666
The patient is gone!

414
01:06:49,868 --> 01:06:52,837
