you know what will happen

421
01:07:43,121 --> 01:07:44,486
Why help them?

422
01:07:45,691 --> 01:07:48,683
Just because we know
what destiny holds for us

423
01:07:48,894 --> 01:07:51,488
Doesn't mean we can escape it

424
01:07:51,797 --> 01:07:52,559
Whether or not they can be saved

425
01:07:52,864 --> 01:07:54,297
depends on their destiny

426
01:08:01,106 --> 01:08:04,200
That ghost really loves
her boyfriend too much

427
01:08:04,443 --> 01:08:06,377
We can only save the woman

428
01:08:06,612 --> 01:08:08,307
I hope she will leave your son alone

429
01:08:51,657 --> 01:08:53,124
Master, someone's moving the corpse!

430
01:10:20,512 --> 01:10:23,777
Joy, help me!

431
01:10:24,249 --> 01:10:25,978
Kill Jack for me!

432
01:10:26,351 --> 01:10:28,285
We love each other

433
01:10:28,620 --> 01:10:30,019
He wants to die

434
01:10:30,255 --> 01:10:32,086
because he wants to be with me!

435
01:10:38,830 --> 01:10:40,821
Lok!

436
01:10:41,633 --> 01:10:42,827
Master!

437
01:10:43,602 --> 01:10:45,502
Joy, you understand

438
01:10:45,871 --> 01:10:47,532
Do you remember
when you were young

439
01:10:47,739 --> 01:10:49,604
Your mom killed your dad
the same way

440
01:10:50,008 --> 01:10:51,475
Because she loved your dad?

441
01:10:51,710 --> 01:10:53,678
She didn't want your dad
to leave you

442
01:10:54,846 --> 01:10:56,177
Love him...

443
01:10:57,616 --> 01:10:59,550
Lok... what are you doing?

444
01:10:59,751 --> 01:11:01,912
Lok, what is it?

445
01:11:02,187 --> 01:11:05,588
Joy, this is love. You know it

446
