454
01:12:41,152 --> 01:12:42,380
Lok...

455
01:12:43,989 --> 01:12:47,925
Don't be afraid. Dad is here

456
01:13:03,108 --> 01:13:05,269
My son didn't hurt anybody!

457
01:13:06,344 --> 01:13:08,505
