484
01:15:13,438 --> 01:15:16,896
Anyone?

485
01:15:17,142 --> 01:15:18,404
Help!

486
01:15:18,710 --> 01:15:20,507
Anyone? Help...

487
01:15:54,979 --> 01:15:59,006
Lok...

488
01:16:08,927 --> 01:16:10,189
Lok

489
01:16:15,400 --> 01:16:19,359
Lok...

490
01:16:44,429 --> 01:16:45,327
Miss!

