01:17:00,678 --> 01:17:01,736
Joy...

492
01:17:04,516 --> 01:17:05,778
Joy...

493
01:17:17,595 --> 01:17:26,401
Joy...

494
01:17:45,590 --> 01:17:47,490
We love each other

495
01:17:50,829 --> 01:17:52,296
Joy, help me!

496
01:17:53,064 --> 01:17:55,089
Your mom killed your dad
the same way

497
01:17:55,934 --> 01:17:57,162
I'm Yau Yin Ping

498
01:17:59,037 --> 01:18:00,937
Kill Jack for me!

499
01:18:01,639 --> 01:18:03,300
Joy, no!

500
01:18:04,542 --> 01:18:05,839
Help me!

501
01:18:07,445 --> 01:18:09,640
