502
01:18:09,848 --> 01:18:11,577
So this is the only way
we can come together

503
01:18:11,816 --> 01:18:13,579
We love each other

504
01:18:16,721 --> 01:18:18,746
We just want together!

505
01:18:19,390 --> 01:18:21,085
The girl looked at us

506
01:18:23,161 --> 01:18:24,287
Joy

507
01:18:33,271 --> 01:18:36,035
Joy, help me, please!

508
01:18:37,108 --> 01:18:39,008
Help me, please!

509
01:18:49,988 --> 01:18:52,252
Help...

510
01:18:52,690 --> 01:18:54,624
Open up...

511
01:18:59,964 --> 01:19:02,228
Open up!

512
01:21:03,554 --> 01:21:05,545
I'm here to kill him for you

513
01:21:05,857 --> 01:21:07,290
Let go of Joy!

514
01:21:43,161 --> 01:21:44,492
